ygData.messageBody:
Hello.
I am a 27 yr old GWM. I live in South Carolina. I have a lev 24 DEF Necro,
Named Wampir Keogh, and a lev 7 BAR Sham Named Windom. Both are on the
Bristlebane server. I like the idea of starting a GLBT guild but what would
be wrong with starting the guild on any server that wants it. Sure the new
Race War server would be a great place to start, but why not have a branch
chapters in all of the others.

Iv already seen plenty of people say they have Bristlebane char to be able to
start one. Just my 2cp

Any way If you fell like it look me up online or you can email me
wampir@....

Thanks
Jamie

P.S. I get alot of junk email if you want me to read yours put my name in the
subject wampir. Elce I may miss it.

Thanks
Jamie
